Installation

**************************
Requirements
**************************

* Java 6 or above
* Preferably more than 1 GB RAM 
* Apache Ant -- http://ant.apache.org/ (if compiling from source)


**************************
Steps
**************************

Let's call the root directory PROJ_ROOT.

1. Run ant in PROJ_ROOT
     $ cd PROJ_ROOT
     $ ant dist

2. Fangorn distribution is compiled and copied into PROJ_ROOT/dist

3. PROJ_ROOT/dist/fangorn is now your distribution root (DIST_ROOT) folder

4. All commands in the README file, unless otherwise specified, must be 
   executed from DIST_ROOT
